PrecisAmendment to the BREWERY REGULATIONS extending the time for payment of excise duties by brewers for eleven months of the year to the second-to-last business day of the month following that in which the beer was produced.

precis:
Amendment to the BREWERY REGULATIONS extending the time for payment of
excise duties by brewers for eleven months of the year to the
second-to-last business day of the month following that in which the beer
was produced.
